This world's Anna is in COMMAND?
Huh... Knowing us Annas, these folks
must've been through the wringer.

Yeah, I've heard about my sisters in
other worlds—women with the same
name and face as mine...$k$pOh, you want to know how it works?
Well...that information doesn't come
free, y'know!

Some children like sweets, some like
books. Whatever the case, I've got it
on sale! Happiness, at a bargain!

Would it be a problem if I opened up
shop nearby? And not just to make
a quick buck, I swear! ...Heh, heh.

I'm all for living in a peaceful place.
Fewer bandits, fewer troubles, I say.
Especially when transporting goods!

I'm Anna—and I have the finest wares
this side of $Nf's.
Record profits!

That's one step closer to becoming
a master merchant!

Yikes. Nothing comes free, I suppose.
I'll try harder.

A pleasure doing business. I hope this
little arrangement continues to bear
fruit for us both!

Need of some wares? Fear not! Anna
the Merchant, at your service. I've got
the best deals anywhere—count on it!

Listen up! I just came up with the
best idea for a tournament... What
do you think about...arm wrestling?$k$pThere are so many famous Heroes
here, it'd be a shame to let all that
star power go to waste, right?$k$pA lot of 'em aren't too bad to look
at either... Put a pretty face on some
merch, and you're in the money!$k$pHuh? What're the profits for? ...Oh!
Well...all for the Order of What's-It...
oh, Heroes! Yeah—trust me!$k$pJust prepare yourself, because you're
about to have more funds than your
Commander'll know what to do with!

Stick with me, and I'll fill your treasury. That's the Anna guarantee! (Huh, I should write that down...)

What's gonna be the next big thing around here? Y'know, the thing that'll really draw in the coin.
